text: The Uzbek Wikipedia () is the Uzbek-language edition of Wikipedia. This edition was started in December 2003. As of October 2015, it is the 44th largest edition of Wikipedia by number of articles.Wikimedia list of Wikipedias and their statistics.. Retrieved 25 October 2015. As of July 2013, it has over 127,000 articles.List of Wikipedias on Meta-Wiki. ==References== ==Other websites== *Uzbek Wikipedia main page Category:Wikipedias Category:Websites established in 2003
